{"tid":2049306,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警「睇唔到」消防車 一段片影響判決","createTime":"2020-06-03T11:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T11:18:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3514f1f33197b6ca0f20bde8a1669ab5ef1e4dd6","tid":2049306,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:10:48.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200603/DCCLQ3G5MQ2OJSMWUPCOPVJAW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200603%2FDCCLQ3G5MQ2OJSMWUPCOPVJAW4%2F&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BO8Zsbf427MOg7dSrB3lcR0%3D&h=e30a7702\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200603%2FDCCLQ3G5MQ2OJSMWUPCOPVJAW4%2F&h=5860af23\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200603/DCCLQ3G5MQ2OJSMWUPCOPVJAW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n警「睇唔到」消防車<br />\n一段片影響判決<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JYQ5YRMO7LR427RFH45CTJ3FKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJYQ5YRMO7LR427RFH45CTJ3FKE.jpg&h=00cdf054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民從高空拍到被告案發時曾遭暴力對待，事後他被打致頭破血流。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本案被告林子浩另一脫罪關鍵，在於辯方呈堂片段顯示案發時一度有消防車打橫停泊在馬路上，凸顯警員作供有疑點。法官沈小民接納辯方片段準確反映事實，認為片段或能否定警員證供的關鍵環節、即二人聲稱觀察被告時視線沒有受阻。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：反送中暴動案 首名被告脫罪 官斥警隱瞞真相<br />\n<br />\n從高空拍下被告遭制服的片段，應在他遭警員追上後、即案發當日下午約4時拍攝，被告的中學同學則於下午4時半至5時間從Telegram收到該片段。辯方曾問警員楊運球，指有消防車「打橫攔住成條路」，是警方為截。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TXX3EXSFXHDLWY7ORYTYVATLEA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTXX3EXSFXHDLWY7ORYTYVATLEA.gif&h=aab6935b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n辯方呈堂片段顯示案發時一度有消防車打橫停泊在馬路，凸顯兩名警員作供有疑點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理應察覺消防車在場<br />\n<br />\n沈官指消防車停泊一事相當矚目，在場警員應察覺該車存在，但一名警員供稱沒印象，另一警則謂沒有此事，質疑法庭如何照單全收他們的證供。控方曾反對將片段呈堂，但沈官指，若有人造假將消防車輸入畫面以支持辯方說法，則該。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，負責查案的探員稱案發後曾到現場索取閉路電視片段，報告卻寫上沒發現相關片段，但他在辯方盤問下承認，現場附近的基協中學確有閉路電視鏡頭，惟警方從沒向校方索取片段。沈官認為中學門外的閉路電視應拍到。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭語霆"},{"pid":"d5f71b5390bdfc285d5cad8a9a8eec052a0d3b29","tid":2049306,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3fb1c1b313dc461995a3040d587c7dee6b9f53","tid":2049306,"uid":134213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"啲省略號係做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d6d2dcf0c7375ae1090b2bab728eadc9db7a4b","tid":2049306,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:15:11.000Z","msg":"dribble yeung 楊運球"},{"pid":"650d3ae76fe5c5429426c51a08e679f786ba4992","tid":2049306,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca3fb1c1b313dc461995a3040d587c7dee6b9f53","tid":2049306,"uid":134213,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:14:54.000Z","msg":"啲省略號係做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T11:18:25.000Z","msg":"係樓豬想我哋訂閱蘋果自己入link睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}